  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Our primary hypothesis is that bile acid sequestrant colesevelam and the antidiabetic drug
      metformin potentiates the secretion of the gut hormone glucagon-like peptide 1 (GLP-1).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
